    What is hamburger menu in Mobile?
    Its function is to toggle a menu (sometimes referred to as a hamburger menu) or navigation bar between being collapsed behind the button or displayed on the screen. The icon which is associated with this widget, consisting of three horizontal bars, is also known as the collapsed menu icon.

    What is a mobile website burger menu?
    They hide important content. First and most fundamentally, hamburger menus hide critically important content that could be visible to a visitor at a glance. They force users to click twice, usually on every page, to discover what content is available and to navigate to it.18-Oct-2023
